autumn.lang.compiler.errors

Enum ErrorCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ErrorCode>
      • autumn.lang.compiler.errors.ErrorCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ErrorCode>

    public enum ErrorCode
extends java.lang.Enum<ErrorCode>
    An instance of this enum identifies the type of a compile-time error.

    Note: The names of these constants are intended to infer their meaning.

    Warning: Constants may herein be added, deleted, or renamed in the future.
